FastPattern.description: NullAlert: pptpd, CTRL couldn't read packet
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: CTRL: couldn't read packet header \(exit\)[\s\x00]*$

FastPattern.description: NullAlert: pptpd, CTRL EOF or bad error
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: CTRL: EOF or bad error reading ctrl packet length\.[\s\x00]*$

FastPattern.description: NullAlert: pptpd, CTRL Fatal error reading
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: CTRL: Fatal error reading control message in disconnect sequence[\s\x00]*$

FastPattern.description: NullAlert: pptpd, CTRL GRE read/write faile
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: CTRL: GRE read or PTY write failed \(gre,pty\)=\(\d+,\d+\)[\s\x00]*$

FastPattern.description: NullAlert: pptpd, CTRL Ignored a SET LINK
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: CTRL: Ignored a SET LINK INFO packet with real ACCMs![\s\x00]*$

FastPattern.description: NullAlert: pptpd, CTRL PTY read/write faile
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: CTRL: PTY read or GRE write failed \(pty,gre\)=\(\d+,\d+\)[\s\x00]*$

FastPattern.description: NullAlert: pptpd, CTRL Unexpected control message
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: CTRL: Unexpected control message \d+ in disconnect sequence[\s\x00]*$
^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: GRE: Bad checksum from pppd\.[\s\x00]*$
^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: GRE: Discarding (?:duplicate|out of order) packet[\s\x00]*$

FastPattern.description: NullAlert: pptpd, GRE read network/pty failed
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: GRE: read *\(fd=\d+,buffer=[a-f\d]+,len=\d+\) from (?:network|PTY) failed: status = -?\d+ error =.*
^\d+ [-\w.]+ rttable\.\d+: signal tmrouted; (?:received routestat event|xref changes)[\s\x00]*$
^\d+ [-\w.]+ pptpd\.\d+\[\d+\]: CTRL: Session timed out, ending call

FastPattern.matcher: ^(\d+) ([-\w.]+) (0-ppp\d+\.\d+)\[\d+\]: (\S+): Can't reopen pipe to command substitution \(fd (\d+)\): (.+?)[\s\x00]*$
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ 0-ppp\d+\.\d+\[\d+\]: \S+: Can't reopen pipe to command substitution \(fd \d+\):

FastField.defaultValue: Can't reopen pipe to command substitution
$4: Can't reopen pipe to command substitution (fd $5), $6

FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+ tmauthd\.\d+\[\d+\]: (?:501 Method not implemented|404 invalid url)
^\d+ [-\w.]+ admin.\d+\[\d+\]: Login failure for user \S+ from [\d.]+
